<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='902744' id='t-902744'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='906216' id='t-906216'>Bruno Giussani: Elizabeth Lev, thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:20
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='909211' id='t-909211'>Elizabeth, you mentioned
this whole issue of pornography,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='913091' id='t-913091'>too many nudes and too many
