<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='918555' id='t-918555'>in the eyes of the time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='920444' id='t-920444'>But actually the story is bigger.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='922074' id='t-922074'>It's not just touching up
and covering up some of the figures.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='925118' id='t-925118'>This work of art was almost
destroyed because of that.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='928383' id='t-928383'>Elizabeth Lev: The effect
of the Last Judgment was enormous.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='931432' id='t-931432'>The printing press made sure
that everybody saw it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='934406' id='t-934406'>And so, this wasn't something
