<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='942207' id='t-942207'>of editorials and complaints,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='944155' id='t-944155'>saying to the Church,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='945347' id='t-945347'>&quot;You can't possibly tell us
how to live our lives.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='947946' id='t-947946'>Did you notice you have
pornography in the Pope's chapel?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='951310' id='t-951310'>And so after complaints and insistence</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='953794' id='t-953794'>of trying to get this work destroyed,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='956534' id='t-956534'>it was finally the year
that Michelangelo died</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='958719' id='t-958719'>that the Church finally
found a compromise,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='960824' id='t-960824'>a way to save the painting,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='962379' id='t-962379'>and that was in putting up
